{
  "stem": "10818.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the next summer, we went to be counselors in a camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we came back from that, I just beat the bushes around Yale.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And seeing that I knew the-- I had been there for a year, I knew where to go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And found a job in the political science department, with the Center of International-- it was then the Institute of International Studies.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, it turned out that my boss who hired me as a research assistant and a secretary, if necessary-- when I told my mother this, she said, I told you two years ago, when you started going to Yale, to look up this man.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His wife is related, you know-- six degrees of separation-- to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and you should have looked him up then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, children never do what their parents tell them to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I hadn't looked him up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we got to be very good friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And next week is his 85th birthday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I must write him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He-- and he's still alive and active and--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until I retired.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] The story is that the Center of International-- the Institute of International Studies got into some sort of a disagreement with the Yale administration and were asked to leave.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so the whole-- I mean, it decimated the political science department.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But about-- more than a dozen professors left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this man, Professor Gabriel Almond, one day called me into his office and said, we're all moving to Princeton.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you want to come along?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Boom!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was the year that Frank graduated from music school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we knew that in order for him to work, we had to be in commuting distance from New York.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he didn't want to particularly be on Long Island.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
